вЂЄfor brain food?

147
00:11:07,667 --> 00:11:08,501
вЂЄExcuse me?

148
00:11:08,584 --> 00:11:09,669
вЂЄHow is your memory so good?

149
00:11:09,752 --> 00:11:14,382
вЂЄOh, well, I do try to eat a lot of fish.
вЂЄI like mackerel in particular.

150
00:11:15,257 --> 00:11:17,259
