вЂЄand learn how to bend the rules instead.

152
00:11:20,304 --> 00:11:21,472
вЂЄBe flexible.

153
00:11:22,473 --> 00:11:24,683
вЂЄJust write it off
вЂЄas a company dinner expense.

154
00:11:28,020 --> 00:11:28,854
вЂЄYes, sir.

155
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:31,524
