вЂЄThis looks useful, right?

176
00:12:39,175 --> 00:12:41,719
вЂЄIt's easy to carry around
вЂЄand seems effective.

177
00:12:42,928 --> 00:12:44,013
вЂЄIs it for you?

178
00:12:44,096 --> 00:12:45,347
вЂЄI think it's for women.

179
00:12:45,431 --> 00:12:47,391
вЂЄMin-ji's birthday is coming up.

180
